<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2><%= @user.first_name %>, you have <%= @user.new_packages.size %> <%= 'package'.pluralize(@user.new_packages.size) %> awaiting pickup.</h2>
    <p>Please come to the mail room and pick <%= 'it'.pluralize(@user.new_packages.size) %>
    up as soon as possible.</p>
    <p>If you have already picked up the <%= 'package'.pluralize(@user.new_packages.size) %>, 
    please log in and mark that you have done so.</p>
    <p>Have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>
